  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895240/extras/d535516e262edab7dfa36f83652d264f.avif?t=1646295414\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br><br>John went for an internship at a shop on a tropical island, but it's more like a holiday.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hang out with the girls!<br></li><li>Get lost on an island!<br></li><li>Enjoy your vacations!<br></li><li>Have fun on the beach!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Depending on your reading speed).",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1895240/extras/d535516e262edab7dfa36f83652d264f.avif?t=1646295414\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br><br>John went for an internship at a shop on a tropical island, but it's more like a holiday.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hang out with the girls!<br></li><li>Get lost on an island!<br></li><li>Enjoy your vacations!<br></li><li>Have fun on the beach!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Depending on your reading speed).",
